---
// Neobrutal How It Works component explaining the platform workflow
---

<section class="py-24 bg-black">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-yellow-400 mb-6">
        HOW FAIRMIND WORKS
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-yellow-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-bold">
        A COMPREHENSIVE 5-STEP PROCESS TO ENSURE YOUR AI SYSTEMS ARE FAIR, TRANSPARENT, AND COMPLIANT
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Process Steps -->
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Connection Line -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-yellow-400 transform -translate-y-1/2"></div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-8 lg:gap-4">
        
        <!-- Step 1: Data Upload -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-black p-8 rounded-none border-2 border-yellow-400 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(255,255,0,1)] text-center lg:text-left">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-400 rounded-none border-2 border-black flex items-center justify-center mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-6 shadow-[3px_3px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-xl">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-yellow-400 mb-4">UPLOAD & VALIDATE</h3>
            <p class="text-yellow-400 mb-4 font-bold">
              UPLOAD YOUR DATASETS AND MODELS. OUR SYSTEM AUTOMATICALLY VALIDATES DATA QUALITY, STRUCTURE, AND IDENTIFIES POTENTIAL BIAS SOURCES.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-yellow-400 space-y-1 font-bold">
              <li>• DATA QUALITY ASSESSMENT</li>
              <li>• SCHEMA VALIDATION</li>
              <li>• BIAS SOURCE IDENTIFICATION</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2: Bias Analysis -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-black p-8 rounded-none border-2 border-yellow-400 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(255,255,0,1)] text-center lg:text-left">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-400 rounded-none border-2 border-black flex items-center justify-center mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-6 shadow-[3px_3px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-xl">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-yellow-400 mb-4">BIAS DETECTION</h3>
            <p class="text-yellow-400 mb-4 font-bold">
              COMPREHENSIVE BIAS ANALYSIS USING STATISTICAL METHODS, CUSTOM RULES, AND LLM-POWERED INSIGHTS TO IDENTIFY FAIRNESS ISSUES.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-yellow-400 space-y-1 font-bold">
              <li>• STATISTICAL PARITY ANALYSIS</li>
              <li>• CUSTOM FAIRNESS RULES</li>
              <li>• LLM-POWERED INSIGHTS</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3: Explainability -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-black p-8 rounded-none border-2 border-yellow-400 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(255,255,0,1)] text-center lg:text-left">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-400 rounded-none border-2 border-black flex items-center justify-center mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-6 shadow-[3px_3px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-xl">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-yellow-400 mb-4">EXPLAINABILITY</h3>
            <p class="text-yellow-400 mb-4 font-bold">
              GENERATE TRANSPARENT EXPLANATIONS USING SHAP, DALEX, AND LIME TO UNDERSTAND MODEL DECISIONS AND FEATURE IMPORTANCE.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-yellow-400 space-y-1 font-bold">
              <li>• SHAP ANALYSIS</li>
              <li>• DALEX EXPLANATIONS</li>
              <li>• FEATURE IMPORTANCE</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4: Simulation -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-black p-8 rounded-none border-2 border-yellow-400 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(255,255,0,1)] text-center lg:text-left">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-400 rounded-none border-2 border-black flex items-center justify-center mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-6 shadow-[3px_3px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-xl">4</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-yellow-400 mb-4">SIMULATION & TESTING</h3>
            <p class="text-yellow-400 mb-4 font-bold">
              RUN BIAS SIMULATIONS TO TEST DIFFERENT SCENARIOS, DEMOGRAPHIC SHIFTS, AND DEPLOYMENT IMPACTS BEFORE GOING LIVE.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-yellow-400 space-y-1 font-bold">
              <li>• SCENARIO MODELING</li>
              <li>• IMPACT ASSESSMENT</li>
              <li>• RISK MITIGATION</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 5: Monitoring -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-black p-8 rounded-none border-2 border-yellow-400 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(255,255,0,1)] text-center lg:text-left">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-400 rounded-none border-2 border-black flex items-center justify-center mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-6 shadow-[3px_3px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-xl">5</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-yellow-400 mb-4">MONITORING & COMPLIANCE</h3>
            <p class="text-yellow-400 mb-4 font-bold">
              CONTINUOUS MONITORING WITH REAL-TIME ALERTS, COMPLIANCE TRACKING, AND AUTOMATED REPORTING FOR REGULATORY REQUIREMENTS.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-yellow-400 space-y-1 font-bold">
              <li>• REAL-TIME MONITORING</li>
              <li>• COMPLIANCE TRACKING</li>
              <li>• AUTOMATED REPORTING</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
